title: Morning Joe 6/30/21
description: A Board of Elections error in the tabulation of the early results in New York City's ranked-choice Democratic mayoral primary has thrown the race into uncertainty, prompting officials to remove preliminary numbers from the elections website hours after posting them.
author: news.podcasts@nbcuni.com (NBC News)
